    "Background": {
      "text": "Bleeding diathesis\nIncreased risk for of bleeding (\nGI\n,\nICH\n, liver hematoma) due to impaired platelet function\nUremic toxins inhibit platelet aggregation\nDisrupts vWF\nPT/PTT normal, but bleeding time elevated",
